the new product should be in the products list

steps.name: I am on the products page
I click on "agregar-producto"
I complete the fields with valid information
I click on "cancelar"
the product should not be in the products list

elements.name: Eliminar producto correctamente

I click "eliminar" on a product
I confirm the deletion
the product should be deleted from products list

elements.name: Cancelar la eliminación de un producto

steps.name: I am on the products page to delete
I click "eliminar" on a product
I dont confirm the deletion
the product should not be deleted from products list
